content.rendered:
BLUELAB WHEY – BlueLab 100% Whey Protein is optimal for muscle support and recovery from training sessions. It’s formulated with a blend of premium protein sources for fast digestion, amazing taste, and easy mixability.

PREMIUM PROTEIN BLEND – BlueLab 100% Whey features an ultra-premium and easy-digesting blend of Whey Protein Isolate, Hydrolyzed Whey Protein, and Whey Protein Concentrate.

LOW CALORIE AND CARB – BlueLab whey protein powder is keto-friendly and works with your diet, not against it.

HIGH PROTEIN – BlueLab packs an incredible 25 grams of protein in each delicious scoop. Try our delectable WheyTella flavor for a yummy hazelnut shake or our classic chocolate and vanilla flavors

SIZE : 2 LBS
